      "text": "भारतीय įरज़वŊ बœक _____________RESERVE BANK OF INDIA______________\nwww.rbi.org.in\nRBI/DCM/2024-25/114 DCM (CC) No.G-2/03.35.01/2024-25 April 01, 2024\nThe Chairman / Managing Director / Chief Executive Officer (All banks having Currency Chests)\nMadam / Dear Sir,\nMaster Direction on Penal Provisions in reporting of transactions / balances at Currency Chests\nIn terms of the Preamble to and Section 45 of the Reserve Bank of India Act, 1934 (RBI",
