    {
      "logical_unit_id": "MD12648_lu22",
      "document_id": "MD12648",
      "title": "(iii) In all the above cases (excepting shortages in chest balances / remittances, shortages",
      "text": "(iii) In all the above cases (excepting shortages in chest balances / remittances, shortages\ndue to pilferage / frauds, counterfeit banknotes detected in chest balances / remittances),\npenal interest shall be levied from the date of inclusion of 'ineligible' amounts in chest\nbalances till the exclusion of such amounts from chest balances.",
